Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.23,0:24:58.53,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遥远未来的生命\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Will the beings of a distant future,
