Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.15,0:25:34.25,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}普通恒星死亡时的炫目光罩转瞬即逝\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The psychedelic death shrouds of ordinary stars are fleeting,
