Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.17,0:25:55.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天狼星 夜空中最亮那颗星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sirius, the brightest star in the night sky,
