Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.44,0:25:59.81,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一颗白矮星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a white dwarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.85,0:26:01.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曾经像太阳一样\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It was once a Sun-like star.
