Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.43,0:26:18.56,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从较大恒星出来的气体\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When the gas from the larger star
