Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.31,0:26:29.17,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最大规模的爆炸会释放\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The greatest burst will release
