Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.71,0:26:36.78,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每一次的爆炸被称为 新星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Each one of those star bursts is called a "nova,"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.71,0:26:36.78,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}Nova：新星
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.82,0:26:40.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在拉丁语中就是 新 的意思\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from the Latin for "new."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.05,0:26:42.96,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一颗质量相当于15个太阳的恒星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A star about 15 times as massive as the Sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.99,0:26:45.92,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比如参宿七 一颗蓝超巨星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one like Rigel, the blue supergiant
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.96,0:26:48.03,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}猎户座的右脚\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that forms the right foot of Orion,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.06,0:26:49.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就有着不同的命运\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}has a different fate in store.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.90,0:26:53.50,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}电子的压力不会使它的坍缩停止\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Its collapse will not be stopped by the pressure of electrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.64,0:26:58.84,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它持续坍缩\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The star will keep falling in on itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.87,0:27:01.87,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直到原子核过度拥挤\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}until its nuclei become so overcrowded
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.91,0:27:04.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始相互排斥\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that they push back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.65,0:27:09.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}参宿七会缩小差不多10万倍\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Rigel will shrink down about 100,000 times,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.72,0:27:13.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直到原子核之间没有距离\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}until there's no space left between the nuclei
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.05,0:27:15.25,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无法再缩小\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it can shrink no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.03,0:27:21.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到那时 它引发\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}At that point, it ignites
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.49,0:27:25.50,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一场更强烈的核反应 超新星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a more powerful nuclear reaction, a supernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.87,0:27:32.40,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大部分的恒星演变\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Most stellar evolution
