Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.54,0:27:36.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是内部的坍缩\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the interior collapse
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.28,0:27:39.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}引发超新星爆炸只需要几秒钟\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that triggers a supernova explosion takes only seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.18,0:27:42.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只剩下一个原子核\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What remains will be an atomic nucleus
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.68,0:27:45.35,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个小城市那么大\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the size of a small city--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.39,0:27:49.22,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}急速旋转的中子星被称为 脉冲星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a rapidly rotating neutron star called a pulsar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.90,0:28:05.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但对于质量超过太阳30倍的恒星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But for a star more than 30 times as massive as the Sun--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.41,0:28:08.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比如参宿二 在猎户座的腰带上\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a star like Alnilam, in Orion's Belt--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.41,0:28:11.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没什么可以阻止它的坍缩\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there will be no stopping its collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.38,0:28:13.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几百万年后\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In a few million years,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.11,0:28:14.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}参宿二燃烧殆尽\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when Alnilam runs out of fuel,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.91,0:28:16.92,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它也会变成超新星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it, too, will go supernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.95,0:28:20.29,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}崩溃的参宿二核心\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The imploding core of Alnilam
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.32,0:28:23.82,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}质量大得 即使核力也不足以承受它的坍缩\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will be so massive that not even nuclear forces
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.82,0:28:26.79,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}质量大得 即使核力也不足以承受它的坍缩\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will be strong enough to hold off its collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.83,0:28:29.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有什么可以抵抗这种引力\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nothing can withstand such gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.73,0:28:32.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}密度如此惊人的恒星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And such a star has an astonishing destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.80,0:28:38.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它会持续坍缩\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It will continues to collapse,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.81,0:28:41.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超越时空的界限\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}crossing a boundary in space-time
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.41,0:28:43.58,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}称为 视界\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}called the "event horizon,"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.41,0:28:43.58,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}即黑洞表面
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.61,0:28:45.64,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们无法看到内部\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond which we cannot see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.68,0:28:47.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当它贯穿那个界限\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When it traverses that frontier,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.78,0:28:51.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}星星从我们的视线 消失得无影无踪\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the star will vanish completely from sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.92,0:28:55.55,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它在黑洞内\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It will be inside a black hole,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.59,0:29:01.96,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那里的引力无比强大 即使光也无法逃脱\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a place where gravity is so strong that nothing, not even light, can escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.99,0:29:11.53,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有一种罕见的恒星有着更戏剧化的命运\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But there's an even more dramatic fate that awaits a rare kind of star
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.56,0:29:13.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的银河系就有一颗\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's one of them in our galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.73,0:29:16.23,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它很不稳定 当它爆炸时\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's so unstable that when it goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.27,0:29:19.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它不会变成新星或者超新星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it won't become a mere nova or supernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.74,0:29:22.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它变成更大的灾难\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It'll become something far more catastrophic...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.27,0:29:24.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}极超新星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a hypernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.58,0:29:27.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我们这辈子就可能发生\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it could happen in our lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.36,0:29:44.26,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}澳洲内陆是地球上最好的星空观测地点之一\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are few places on Earth to get a better view of the night sky than the Australian Outback.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.07,0:29:48.40,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有建筑物\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No buildings,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.43,0:29:51.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没车 没路灯 什么都没有\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}no cars, streetlights, nothing out here;
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.37,0:29:53.20,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有星光\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just lots of starlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.24,0:29:55.57,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶尔有几只袋鼠\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the occasional kangaroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.61,0:29:59.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这里 你可以非常好的观察银河系\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can get a particularly good view of the Milky Way from down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.11,0:30:00.78,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}银河的中心\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The center of our galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.81,0:30:02.41,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}高悬在空中\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}rises high in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.45,0:30:04.45,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拱形穿过天空\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it arches across the heavens
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.48,0:30:07.12,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像黑夜的脊梁\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like the backbone of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.15,0:30:08.89,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的银河系是个螺旋星云\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We live in a spiral galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.92,0:30:10.89,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们看向银河时\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And when we look at the Milky Way,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.92,0:30:14.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们可以看到螺旋圆盘中几十亿颗恒星发出的光\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we're seeing light from billions of stars in its spiral disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.89,0:30:17.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这样美丽的夜空下\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And under this beautiful dark sky,
