Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.97,0:30:24.07,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有些黑色的斑块遮掩了星光\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are dark patches, breaks in the starlight.
