Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.56,0:35:09.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果附近有太阳系\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If there are nearby solar systems
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.76,0:35:14.07,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伴随有生命的行星 它们的死期到了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with planets harboring life, their days are numbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.10,0:35:17.40,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}极超新星喷出大量的辐射\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A hypernova spews so much radiation into space--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.44,0:35:20.71,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不只光 还有X射线 伽马射线\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}not just light, but X-rays and gamma rays--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.74,0:35:22.74,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几十光年外的行星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that planets that are dozens
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.78,0:35:25.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或者甚至几百光年外的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or perhaps hundreds of light-years away
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.15,0:35:27.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都会丧失它们的大气层\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}could be stripped of their atmospheres
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.11,0:35:29.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后被死亡辐射笼罩\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and bathed in deadly radiation.
